{"tid":890813,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"公廁企格既尷尬design","createTime":"2018-11-05T15:17:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T08:21:12.000Z","uid":204845,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"47b4cfb1ab0472f86b72aa37c17a282846b0f2f4","tid":890813,"uid":204845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T15:17:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d3EafNw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd3EafNw.jpg&h=2fda8838&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔知點解去親呢d公廁企格，就會好自然咁企上去個鐵網格(相信好多人都係咁)，但係條jer同塊鐵板距離太近，d尿會反彈番黎，而且鐵網格有其他人既尿漬。相反，如果企係鐵網格出面屙尿，一定會屙到鐵網格，又驚整污糟下一個企上去既人。所以，我覺得鐵網格本身唔係design俾人企上去，係防止踩落尿槽既裝置，但係有第一個人企左上去，以後就有千千萬萬既人企上去屙尿。鐵網格的確發揮到防踩尿槽既效果，但係就造成&ldquo;企唔企上去好&rdquo;既尷尬。"},{"pid":"0415ee8af5d17aa2229343473caf79171e601279","tid":890813,"uid":94452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T15:20:26.000Z","msg":"唔會企"},{"pid":"29cc3d7981519796aeac72057e7f9f9fee90675b","tid":890813,"uid":187902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T15:21:32.000Z","msg":"咁d廢老咪滴到成地都係囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"852fc6232d9843e6ab6089b3f51987618c8948a5","tid":890813,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T15:22:14.000Z","msg":"我覺得鐵網格本身唔係design俾人企上去，係防止踩落尿槽既裝置<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1af22a3865dc37fd64193cfbd1ac8dcc8d6a268","tid":890813,"uid":83016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T15:23:56.000Z","msg":"其實係用黎企"},{"pid":"6dec69c756e17abc4e5f4495738487da68c1298f","tid":